snippet.title: JellyCar iPhone - First Trailer
snippet.description:
video of the first release version of "JellyCar" for the iPhone.  This is a full port of the game, with smooth physics, simple and intuitive controls, and 12 levels to play (with full music and sound - optional of course).

more info at walaber.com
